description: The full secret identifier and attributes are provided in the response. No values are returned for the secrets. This operations requires the secrets/list permission.

maxresults.description: Maximum number of results to return in a page. If not specified, the service will return up to 25 results.

value.description: A response message containing a list of secrets in the key vault along with a link to the next page of secrets.

nextlink.description: The URL to get the next set of secrets.
